{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/employment/retraining","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Retraining","meta_description":"Advice and recommendations for retraining.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p>Retraining is an active employment policy tool that enables individuals to obtain a qualification for a new job or to maintain an existing job. The determination of the content is based on the current qualifications, health status, abilities and experiences of a person to be retrained. Retraining is provided by the Labour Office competent according to the place of residence of the job seeker.</p>\n<p>All necessary information can be found on the <a href=\"https://www.uradprace.cz/rekvalifikace-1\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">website</a> of the Labor Office.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/retraining"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-06T07:32:48+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation_type":{"name":"Employment","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"work"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[{"question":"Will the Labour Office pay me for a retraining?","value":"Yes, if the prescribed conditions are met."},{"question":"Will the course be chosen by the employment office, or can I choose it myself?","value":"Both are possible. If you do not know, you can ask the Labour Office for help in choosing a suitable course for you."},{"question":"I chose a course that I don't enjoy. What now?","value":"If you are a self-payer, nothing will happen and you will lose money for an unfinished course. If the retraining is paid for you by the Labour Office, you will pay the costs by yourself."}],"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-11-06T16:11:06+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Employment","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation":[{"id":"3872e0d0-90c3-5b68-b0c4-03987ad099d1","title":"Home office","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/home-office"}},{"id":"309c223d-2475-58de-bf5d-298398cad794","title":"Hygienic measures in the workplace","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/hygienic-measures-workplace"}},{"id":"a7f20be3-3a34-58b7-9714-45a043c46f27","title":"eNeschopenka","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/eneschopenka"}},{"id":"8222ed2e-b8bd-5f5f-afc7-3d366af361ac","title":"Wage compensation","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/wage-compensation"}},{"id":"8c196506-f43f-5b68-99a1-585972e45b75","title":"Job interviews","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/job-interviews"}},{"id":"53f19155-d696-553a-8feb-d83685c899b5","title":"The protection of employees","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/protection-employees"}},{"id":"55d2f54b-68b2-5643-899e-5a8bc2c06da1","title":"Legal support","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/legal-support"}},{"id":"f19da8d2-1daa-53e1-8d8e-1a2e5aa0833d","title":"Job loss","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/job-loss"}},{"id":"0ac9f0f6-3202-5c41-a40f-f948d121fb1b","title":"Retraining","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/retraining"}},{"id":"6e30c948-4d3e-5800-8448-1d1406295f58","title":"Corporate events","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/corporate-events"}},{"id":"e5b9bcb3-01f9-58ba-b279-d7cc1c304a11","title":"On the job training","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/job-training"}},{"id":"2cc61c5d-abc8-568f-a98e-7b30c46de95f","title":"Company canteens","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/company-canteens"}},{"id":"d5b98b8b-d756-5e66-b21b-e06aaf2d50c6","title":"Shift work","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/shift-work"}},{"id":"509091ec-f258-51ef-b169-41f5424ba09a","title":"Infected colleague","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/infected-colleague"}}]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/situations/employment/retraining","lan